<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA611_03_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema611_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema611_03_ih_0001">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1">
          <span lang="y">3÷2의 몫을 두 가지 방법으로 나타내려고 합니다. 그림을 보고</span>
          <span class="empty_box nemo"></span>
          <span lang="y">안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center">
          <div class="question_col">
            <span lang="y" class="label_method">방법1</span>
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA611_03_IH/0001_01.png" alt="" />
              <p class="text1">1</p>
              <p class="text2">1</p>
              <p class="text3">1</p>
              <p class="text4">÷2</p>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area">
              3÷2=
              <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
                <math-field data-answer-single="1" text-align="center" placeholder="&nbsp;" class="w_80"></math-field>
              </div>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="1" text-align="center" placeholder="&nbsp;" class="w_80"></math-field>
                </div>
                <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="2" text-align="center" placeholder="&nbsp;" class="w_80"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="question_col">
            <span lang="y" class="label_method">방법2</span>
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA611_03_IH/0001_02.png" alt="" />
              <p class="text1">1</p>
              <p class="text2">1</p>
              <p class="text3">1</p>
              <p class="text4">÷2</p>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area">
              3÷2=
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="3" text-align="center" placeholder="&nbsp;" class="w_80"></math-field>
                </div>
                <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="2" text-align="center" placeholder="&nbsp;" class="w_80"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p class="flex align_center gap_4">
                  <span lang="y" class="label_method">방법1</span>
                  <span lang="y">3개 중에서 2개를 1개씩 나눈 다음 남은 1개를 2로 똑같이 나누어 몫을 나타냈습니다.</span>
                </p>
                <div class="flex align_center gap_0">
                  ➔ 3÷2=1<span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>2</span></span>
                </div>
                <p class="flex align_center gap_4">
                  <span lang="y" class="label_method">방법2</span>
                  <span lang="y">3개를 각각 2로 똑같이 나누어 몫을 나타냈습니다.</span>
                </p>
                <div class="flex align_center gap_0">
                  ➔ 3÷2=<span class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>2</span></span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
